transcripts: Who doesn't love a smoothie? I'm gonna show you how you can use your magic bullet to whip up a healthy breakfast. We're going to start with one banana, some strawberries, blueberries, ice, and a little bit of our super food protein boost to give it a little extra flavor and some protein.  We're going to use almond milk to fill it up and all you have to do is attach the cross blade and use the lock on technique. And that's it, now you  have a healthy smoothie that you can have for breakfast. Mmm you guys are going to love this one.
